# Override the user's global gitignore: in this repo `.claude/` is project
# infrastructure (skills, commands, headless settings) and MUST be tracked.
# Keep personal/local overrides untracked.
!.claude/
!.claude/**
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/.session/
.claude/logs/

# Same idea for `.factory/` — machine-readable contract for the agent factory.
!.factory/
!.factory/**
.factory/report.json
